Cell["\<\
pmin=0.75 jump
pmin=1 does not jump
\[CapitalLambda]0=2 does not jump
\[CapitalLambda]0=1 jumps
pmin=5 gives weird jumps in rig 20, among others.

Jumping starts to happen when a new solution for the next lambda value is \
exactly the same as the previous result. Due to failure to find a solution, \
so the old is returned again?\
\>", "Text",
